    <Label name="lblAbout" id="da15bc1a-99ab-4a3c-8e6e-a33a9b42b780">
        <caption>The BaseSchema is available to all JADE Developers, however you may not make alterations to the source code.  Use undocumented features of BaseSchema at your own risk - however you can request that they be considered for documentation in a future release of BaseSchema.  Please send any queries, feature suggestions or possible faults by email to baseschema@jadeworld.com.</caption>
